# 🎉 Plann-Easly

**Plann-Easly** is a smart event management platform that simplifies planning and organizing events by bringing venues, catering, decorations, entertainment, and other event services together in one place.

Whether you're organizing a birthday party, college farewell, corporate event, anniversary, or family gathering, Plann-Easly helps you plan everything within your budget through an intuitive and user-friendly interface.

---

## ✨ Features

* 📅 Create and manage events
* 🏛️ Venue selection and recommendations
* 🍽️ Food and catering management
* 🎈 Decoration theme selection
* 🎵 Music & entertainment booking
* 📸 Photography & videography services
* 💰 Real-time budget calculator
* 📊 Smart event dashboard
* 🤖 AI-powered recommendations (planned)
* 🛍️ Vendor marketplace (planned)

---

