## ⚙️ Installation

Clone the repository:

```bash
git clone https://github.com/AshwinSharma0/easy-palanning.git
```

Move into the project:

```bash
cd easy-palanning
```

Install dependencies:

```bash
cd apps/web
npm install
```

Start the development server:

```bash
npm run dev
```

