---

## 💡 Problem Statement

Planning an event usually requires coordinating multiple vendors, comparing prices, managing bookings, and staying within budget. This process is often time-consuming and confusing.

Plann-Easly aims to solve this by providing a single platform where users can plan, customize, and manage their entire event seamlessly.

---

## 👥 Target Users

* Students
* Families
* Colleges & Universities
* Event Organizers
* Startups
* Small Businesses
* Corporate Teams

---

## 📈 Vision

To become an all-in-one event planning platform that makes organizing events simple, affordable, and stress-free by connecting users with trusted vendors and smart planning tools.

